![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2b9e4f88-c927-422c-8c69-965c8c106c39/Screenshot_20240610-170239_Chrome.jpg)

Raw opens with shots of Lyra and Iyo entering the building ahead of their match tonight.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cc6e2121-611d-4a58-82b5-4b0230dd27d7/Screenshot_20240610-170357_Chrome.jpg)

Drew McIntyre is out to cut a promo but as soon as he says Damian Priests name. Priest and the Judgement Day come out

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/40a4a1f9-c0fb-4b39-90d4-e01623a4de86/Screenshot_20240610-170608_Chrome.jpg)

Drew McIntyre claims Damian can’t retain his title without the help of the Judgement Day. Damien Priest proposes Finn Balor vs Drew McIntyre tonight.

If Drew McIntyre wins, Judgement Day will be banned from Ringside.

Drew McIntyre says next Monday, he doesn’t want to hear any excuses when he shows up to RAW as World Heavyweight Champion.

“HIT MY MUSIC”

