![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/22b69605-e0a0-4f2f-bd89-3ec702ef9e13/Screenshot_20240610-171223_Chrome.jpg)

"I don't think a gorgeous man like you should be with a woman who makes him call her Mami.

A man like you should be with a girl who calls him Daddy."

Liv Morgan slides a hotel key in Dominik's tights and invites him to her hotel room tonight

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/937b4e63-ad85-407b-af60-00039d4ca10c/Screenshot_20240610_172944.jpg)

*   ## **_IYO SKY DEF. LYRA VALKYRIA_**
    

Very good TV match here with an interference mid way and then Iyo sneaking a win at the end. It didn’t touch the quality of their QotR match. Would like to see then tie it up on a PLE.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/10eae9cf-993a-4c6e-976e-02e779655bdc/Screenshot_20240610_173146.jpg)

Damage CTRL jump Lyra after the match because she’s pinned them all at least once and they hate her.

Katana Chance and Kayden Carter come out to even the odds..

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f80ab200-6a27-4ac9-bd05-a28b42de2de9/Screenshot_20240610_173306.jpg)

Dom tells the rest of Judgement Day that Liv gave him a hotel key. Carlito says THATS COOL but the rest of Judgement Day are horrified.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cfc3fa58-b3cc-4a09-b64a-4ed1596e2217/Screenshot_20240610_173905.jpg)

Sami tells the Alpha Academy he’s sorry they’re stuck in the middle of his issues but he’s telling then again, they don’t have to deal with this.

Otis walks up and Sami wants nothing to do with him. Otis tried to apologize but they’ll see each other in the ring later tonight.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/27e3f8d5-ada7-464b-8b66-b94c2f08c920/Screenshot_20240610_174144.jpg)

Dom tells Damien Priest about the hotel key Liv gave him. But the card is missing from the table.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f36cc367-6646-4993-a991-d3ea18ea7fe8/Screenshot_20240610_180108.jpg)

*   ## **_BRAUN STROWMAN/LWO DEF. JUDGEMENT DAY/CARLITO_**
    

2 segment match with some great action. The match ends when Liv gets involved to distract the LWO and help Dom. She gets shoved onto his lap and she grinds him before Zelima Vega breaks it up.

The distractions lead to Bron Breakker pulling out the win for his team.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7f7d4035-f45a-46b3-9ab9-c794eb9e7507/Screenshot_20240610-180537_Chrome.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3f21c5b2-f1f8-493d-aef6-043b3378523c/Screenshot_20240610_180918.jpg)

Ricochet tells Ilja Dragunov that he knows what Ilja is capable of.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2cb40eff-052a-4b85-bbfe-d7b7060ac39d/Screenshot_20240610_181519.jpg)

Iyo Sky is FREAKING OUT. She’s screaming. “DAMAGE CTRL NEEDS TO CHAAAAANGE!!!”

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5d5ae261-0468-48a7-b8b9-ab63af504b38/Screenshot_20240610_182050.jpg)

Sami Zayn calls Chad Gable a manipulative abuser who he’s going to defeat at Clash at the Castle.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a75955a2-4b35-4505-86b8-a072665327a5/Screenshot_20240610_182106.jpg)

Chad Gable and the Alpha Academy come out. Chad says he and his family are happy. Sami screams does he really think they’re happy?

They’re only gonna be happy once they leave Chad Gable. Gable says nobody is leaving anywhere and he’s going to unleash a new version of Otis on Sami Zayn right now.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ff2a14bb-8a4b-4ed8-af36-f3e4365dc6c0/Screenshot_20240610_183016.jpg)

*   ## **_SAMI ZAYN DEF. OTIS_**
    

Chad Gable wouldn't stop trying to call plays. Otis falls to a distraction Helluva Kick.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c9c4b4b4-ea8f-4e84-9b34-d65fae8a5ff5/Screenshot_20240610_183041.jpg)

Chad Gable slaps Otis. Otis looks like he's finally had enough. But he takes out Sami again.

Gable thinks he's safe but Otis turns the aggression towards Chad Gable instead. He's going to take out Gable but he can't bring himself to hurt his mentor. He huffs off.

Chad Gable has created a monster.

