*   ## _SHAYNA BASZLER AND ZOEY STARK DEF. ISLA DAWN AND ALBA FYRE_
    

Shayna Baszler makes quick work of Alba Fyre to win a tag match for her team tonight.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ebe4f887-e443-425c-8a83-69046396a75d/Screenshot_20240610_184857.jpg)

*   ## **_BRON BREAKKER DEF. ILJA DRAGUNOV_**
    

What an excellent TV match. I NEED the PPV rematch this Saturday. Please. Ilja and Bron Breakker are perfect opponents.

Ilka took Bron Breakker to the limit here. He was presented as an actual threat to Bron Breakker. Thus being presented as a threat to ANYBODY on the roster.

Bron has to put Ilja ribs first through a table, onto the barricade and then 3 SPEARS before he could pin Ilja Dragunov.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/eeb37368-ee09-4821-abc5-bf492edbb706/Screenshot_20240610_190547.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4dd128b8-afa7-4d3a-9326-30f67df27c04/Screenshot_20240610_191302.jpg)

Damian has finally accepted Carlito as part of the crew and Dom finds the card key in his tights again.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/965d95ab-c3e2-4bf6-8299-79a0ad84279a/Screenshot_20240610_191902.jpg)

Sheamus reminds Drew McIntyre to keep his focus on the World Championship this Saturday. Than Sheamus can win Money in the Bank.

Drew asks if Sheamus would give him a heads up on a cash in. Sheamus promises it would be just like old times.

