*   ## **_WWE TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: AWESOME TRUTH DEF. AUTHORS OF PAIN_**
    

New Day attacks Karrion Kross. Distracting AoP enough for the Miz to get a roll up victory

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5f71d2e0-e07e-4e41-a777-1d4cd646e30d/Screenshot_20240610-193205_Chrome.jpg)

It appears Ricochet has been written off. Bron Breakker attacked Ilja Dragunov backstage. Ricochet tried to defend him.

Breakker lawn darts Ricochet into the truck, the way Kevin Nash did Rey Mysterio in WCW. Then Powerslams him off a platform through a windshield.

